===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Elesa (Masters)}}
Elesa forms [[sync pair]]s with {{p|Zebstrika}}, {{p|Rotom}}, {{p|Emolga}}, {{p|Joltik}}, {{p|Togetic}}, and {{form|Thundurus|Therian Forme}} {{p|Thundurus}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Her Emolga and Thundurus are capable of [[Dynamax]]ing. Elesa became a playable sync pair October 17, 2019.

Elesa has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories: the [[PML arc]], [[Legendary Adventures]], and the [[villain arc]].

